24#ifndef FLOAT_H
25#define FLOAT_H
26
27typedef struct float_elt
28{
29 struct float_elt *next;
30 char *id;
31 char *type;
32 char *title;
33 char *shorttitle;
34 char *position;
35 char *number;
36 char *section;
37 char *section_name;
38 short title_used;
39 int defining_line;
40} FLOAT_ELT;
41
42extern void add_new_float (char *id, char *title, char *shorttitle,
43 char *type, char *position);
44extern void current_float_set_title_used (void);
45
46/* Information retrieval about the current float env. */
47extern char *current_float_id (void);
48extern char *current_float_title (void);
49extern char *current_float_shorttitle (void);
50extern char *current_float_type (void);
51extern char *current_float_position (void);
52extern char *current_float_number (void);
53extern char *get_float_ref (char *id);
54
55extern int count_floats_of_type_in_chapter (char *type, char *chapter);
56extern int current_float_used_title (void);
57
58#endif /* not FLOAT_H */
